ex:SENS%20motion%20for%20Healthcare a ex:HealthcareApp,
        ex:InformationObject,
        owl:NamedIndividual ;
    ex:chunk_id 31 ;
    ex:hasActivityOverview "Patients will be provided with a tablet in the room where the motivation app is installed. The app will motivate patients to better self-mobilize by giving them a guided virtual tour of Copenhagen. On the app, patients can follow their own activity overview, see how far in the tour they have come, the number of steps and how much active time they have had, both that day and in the last week"^^xsd:string ;
    ex:hasMotivation "It is recommended to read the user manual before using SENS motion"^^xsd:string ;
    ex:hasMotivationalApp "The motivation app will motivate patients to better self-mobilize by giving them a guided virtual tour of Copenhagen. On the app, patients can follow their own activity overview, see how far in the tour they have come, the number of steps and how much active time they have had, both that day and in the last week"^^xsd:string ;
    ex:hasOnlineVisualizationTool "The motivation app will motivate patients to better self-mobilize by giving them a guided virtual tour of Copenhagen. On the app, patients can follow their own activity overview, see how far in the tour they have come, the number of steps and how much active time they have had, both that day and in the last week"^^xsd:string ;
    ex:hasStaffAccessScreen "Staff will have access to an overview screen, where they can easily get an overview of patients' physical activity, including when patients were last mobilized. This will allow staff to prioritise which patients are most important to help with mobilization"^^xsd:string ;
    ex:hasUserManual "https://files/[DANSK]-Brugermanual-SENS-motion-for-Healthcare.pdf"^^xsd:string .

